            580,
            922,
            611
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Inspecting restrooms after closing time for vagrants/ unauthorized personnel.   \nMonitoring selected areas via CcTV app on smart devices.   \nEnsure flawless equipment operation by finishing preventive maintenance necessities, reading the manufacturer's instructions, troubleshooting malfunctions, organizing for repairs if needed, and assessing new equipment and techniques ",
